  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD FULL GAME TO YOUR WISHLIST</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a world where everyone is damaged one way or another you and your sister live peacefully on a farm. Until someone comes and burns it down. All you have left is your car with a hook. The time to learn how to kill with it is running out. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tear your enemies apart with a hook and finish them with their own weapons.<br></li><li>Fight and rip away the hearts of 2 colossal bosses to gain new abilities.<br></li><li>Explore 4 bizarre biomes.<br></li><li>Fight and fly through a nightmarish tunnel to the beat of incredible tracks by KillTheBarber!, Mezzanine, pqQp.</li></ul><br><strong>Gripper: Prologue</strong> is the start of your own personal story of loss. We turned it into the game to let it go and move on. We hope it will help you too.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/f2a1c376f0ca7b8e78fed76c4953e436.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a world where everyone is damaged one way or another you and your sister live peacefully on a farm. Until someone comes and burns it down. All you have left is your car with a hook. The time to learn how to kill with it is running out. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/6fc6cae2d18ac3dd7c2c2e0a42e019cb.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tear your enemies apart with a hook and finish them with their own weapons.<br></li><li>Fight and rip away the hearts of 2 colossal bosses to gain new abilities.<br></li><li>Explore 4 bizarre biomes.<br></li><li>Fight and fly through a nightmarish tunnel to the beat of incredible tracks by KillTheBarber!, Mezzanine, pqQp.</li></ul><br><strong>Gripper: Prologue</strong> is the start of your own personal story of loss. We turned it into the game to let it go and move on. We hope it will help you too.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.poster.avif?t=1663694793\" width=614 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.webm?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1337240/extras/853fc43db2b74465932b59243b682d84.mp4?t=1663694793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
